#: quests/companions/cq_sam_recruitment:10001
msgctxt "quests/companions/cq_sam_recruitment:10001:DefaultText"
msgid "Now that you have the Acid Steeper part needed to modify SAM, all that remains is to return to the Unreliable and swap it out with the factory default S.U.D.S. Steeper."
msgstr ""

#: quests/companions/cq_sam_recruitment:10003
msgctxt "quests/companions/cq_sam_recruitment:10003:DefaultText"
msgid "You found a defunct sanitation and maintenance automechanical in the supply closet upstairs on the Unreliable. A cursory search of the unit revealed the name, SAM, but little else. ADA may know more."
msgstr ""

#: quests/companions/cq_sam_recruitment:10004
msgctxt "quests/companions/cq_sam_recruitment:10004:DefaultText"
msgid "You found entries on Hawthorne's terminal in the Captain's Quarters regarding his attempts to turn SAM into a combat-capable unit. Hawthorne planned to replace SAM's S.U.D.S. Steeper with an Acid Steeper but never picked up the part from Roseway."
msgstr ""

#: quests/companions/cq_sam_recruitment:10005
msgctxt "quests/companions/cq_sam_recruitment:10005:DefaultText"
msgid "ADA suggested that the ship's former captain, Alex Hawthorne, may have kept information about his attempts to modify or repair SAM on the terminal in the Captain's Quarters."
msgstr ""

#: quests/companions/cq_sam_recruitment:30000
msgctxt "quests/companions/cq_sam_recruitment:30000:DefaultText"
msgid "You installed the Acid Steeper part SAM required for modification, in order to revive the unit with added combat capabilities."
msgstr ""

